name: The Ruby Skull of Nibiru - Galactible™ #25
description:
Holy Annunaki! Congratulations, you’ve discovered Galactible™ #25, the “Ruby Skull of Nibiru!” Hidden within the ancient ruins of Nibiru, lies the enchanted Ruby Skull — rumored to have special powers only known to the holder! Left behind from the first civilization of the Milky Way Galaxy, the Ruby Skull is one of 4 skulls created by the Annunaki. Your mana has been raised by +200,000 bits!

Galactibles™ are one-of-a-kind and minted as 1-of-1. Only 99 will be made! New Galactibles™ drop every week (sorta) on twitter, so give us a follow @Galactibles! Certified authentic and original animations, sound effects, and music made by Pyramid Guy (IG: @pyramidguy), aka Kris Kanaly (TW: @kriskanaly). Galactibles™ ©2022 | galactibles.com
